videos.headline: Nelson explains No. 2 Alabama's approach to McNeese, full season
videos.description: Following a 20-point performance in a 72-64 win, Grant Nelson speaks on the Tide's demeanor in matchup vs. the Cowboys and what their thought process is to make another final-four run.
